0.2.name: wordpress/fixpress
0.2.description:
Heres a simple plugin that fixes the gallery so it validates by pushing the css into <head> and a couple of other little tweaks. Also fixes the comment form by removing the 'aria' bits that wont validate as XHTML.

Now with youtube and googlevideo fixes!
